WEBVTT

00:07.621 --> 00:08.898
Hey, don't you
give me that look.

00:08.899 --> 00:11.590
You know what you did.

00:14.728 --> 00:15.961
Yeah, all right.

00:15.963 --> 00:17.329
Right, I should've
taken you out sooner.

00:17.331 --> 00:18.330
Okay, this one's on me.

00:21.769 --> 00:23.569
Stay.

00:29.276 --> 00:31.777
You're not Steve.
No.

00:32.913 --> 00:35.180
Sorry, buddy. You, uh...
you must be Junior, right?

00:35.182 --> 00:37.449
Yes, sir.
Well, happy, uh...

00:37.451 --> 00:38.917
happy Halloween, Junior.

00:38.919 --> 00:41.920
Uh, you must be Detective
Danny Williams, aka Danno.

00:41.922 --> 00:43.255
Oh, that's funny.

00:43.257 --> 00:45.090
Did, uh... did Steve
tell you to say that?

00:45.092 --> 00:46.425
Yes, he did, sir.
Yeah.

00:46.427 --> 00:48.193
And I heard
about your fall.

00:48.195 --> 00:50.929
Yeah, well, this-- see,
Steve bought a cheap ladder

00:50.931 --> 00:52.264
for our restaurant
because he's cheap.

00:52.266 --> 00:53.732
And if he ordered
a nice ladder,

00:53.734 --> 00:55.100
this wouldn't have
happened. What, uh...

00:55.102 --> 00:56.635
you got a little accident
yourself over here?

00:56.637 --> 00:58.303
Yes, sir.

00:58.305 --> 00:59.571
He responsible or you?

00:59.573 --> 01:00.706
Him, sir.

01:00.708 --> 01:02.407
Yeah.

01:02.409 --> 01:04.242
Where's, uh...
where's Steve?

01:04.245 --> 01:06.111
He, uh... he went up
to the North Shore

01:06.113 --> 01:07.813
to escort Dr. Brown
to the courthouse.

01:07.815 --> 01:09.581
Oh, that's right.

01:09.583 --> 01:12.751
Well, I wasted $75 on
this beautiful mask

01:12.753 --> 01:14.753
and gas money to get
here to scare the guy,

01:14.755 --> 01:16.455
and he didn't even
have the courtesy

01:16.457 --> 01:17.144
to be here when I
got here, right?

01:17.168 --> 01:18.758
I'm sorry, sir.

01:18.759 --> 01:20.792
- Do me a favor.
- Yeah.

01:20.794 --> 01:22.728
You don't have to
call me “sir” so much.

01:22.730 --> 01:23.996
Maybe once every...
every couple sentences

01:23.998 --> 01:25.397
or... no, once every
three minutes.

01:25.399 --> 01:26.798
Something like that
would be fine.

01:26.800 --> 01:28.333
Yes, sir.

01:28.335 --> 01:30.435
Yes. Yeah.

01:30.437 --> 01:32.838
Yeah.

01:32.840 --> 01:35.374
Good to meet you, buddy.
All right, you too.

